hey ppls the phones in my neighborhood weren't working, but der working now. so if any1 tried 2 call  me....sorry. o yeah school was cancled 2day, so i went   sk8boardin w/ my friends from VENICE HIGH.  we played SK8 4 like 1hr.  if u don't know what sk8 is, it's a game where some1 does a trick on der board n da whole group has 2 do da same trick, if some1 messes up der OUT!! i almost won, but i got out when my friend Chase did a Hard-Flip down a 5-stair.  i can hard-flip but not down stairs.  we sk8ed so fuckin hard.  i frontside fliped a 5-stair.  i used 2 b sooo in2 sk8in. i was sponsered 4 a lil bit by ZJ's Boarding House, but really only cuz i worked der.  later we went 2 3rd st n went in dat ripcurl store.  i want 2 learn how 2 surf....i can sk8 n snowboards but i cant surf, im pathetic, lmao.  da reason i never had interest in surfing is bcause im afraid of da ocean. da oceans all dirty n wet, duh, but i h8 going in2 the ocean 2 dry off n den gettin out n my feet r all sandy, i h8 gettin sandy period.  i swear, if a piece of kelp touches me i'll scream.....im such a loser.  i've almost died in da ocean, n i've be terrified of it ever since.  o yeah n fish scare da crap out of me 2, they're ugly little motherfuckers homes.    
so i bought a surfboard n now i need a lessons.  maybe i should have thought of lessons b4 i bought da board....whatever.  so after buyin da board we went 2 Mcdonalds n my fiend Shun (i call him asian invasion)shot spit-wads at these 2 FINE girls named Marra n Marisa i x-changed #'s w/ dem but im not gonna call dem....or should I, i don't know what 2 do.  is it better 2 never have luved some1 , is it worth taking da risk of gettin ur heart broken. im happy w/o luv 4 da time being.....so dat was my day, later ppls.
